{"tid":142434,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個忍屎經歷","createTime":"2017-03-03T17:45:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-04T02:50:42.000Z","uid":53736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6893211820f4a096eef0faa62e7e73345c3a395d","tid":142434,"uid":53736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T17:45:10.000Z","msg":"岩先觀塘食完野，臨走個肚都有d痛，諗住少事忍到番屋企（南區）柯，點知車程無耐。個肚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&rarr;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&rarr;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。已經開始唔多掂。<br />\n諗住旺角一落車就衝過m記開大（深夜唔好問點解唔去其他廁所），然後轉車舒舒服服咁轉車番南區。<br />\n屌m記個老母，24小時m記同我關撚左上面個層<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。我即刻衝出m記。"},{"pid":"37ba081786cb2db8b7ea7ae2a7a71968783469d4","tid":142434,"uid":53736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T17:48:22.000Z","msg":"之後問街邊阿姐最近既廁所係邊，佢同我講係下個路口上斜路（好撚遠）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我決定左直接轉車番屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8040ef62f22f3b07d0facfa21393deb0682538c","tid":142434,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T17:49:56.000Z","msg":"轉小巴？<br />\n附近咪有廁所"},{"pid":"5481e7b3d16268844d568fefd1bb0db01a188517","tid":142434,"uid":53736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T17:53:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>轉小巴？<br />\n附近咪有廁所</blockquote><br />\n個陣無理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成程車忍到無力出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42dda4b7f64eead19078698476c3a9d491463488","tid":142434,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T17:53:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>轉小巴？<br />\n附近咪有廁所</blockquote><br />\n個陣無理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成程車忍到無力出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不過夜晚都係唔好亂去公廁"},{"pid":"d92db4a12a846dd0536ab7031d09794200ec8c98","tid":142434,"uid":26020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T18:06:48.000Z","msg":"學校旅行行山 行到一半急屎 仲要係爛屎個隻 <br />\n最後忍到差唔多山頂先見到有廁所 屌你老母個廁所得個窿 下面全部屎同屎蟲 臭撚到崩 不過最後都柯左"},{"pid":"129d6b7f7cdc75ad8387b9e4224692144b78717c","tid":142434,"uid":84355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T01:10:43.000Z","msg":"有次搭長途旅遊巴，一上車就唔多掂，架車又無廁所，屎急加架車登下登下真係好撚辛苦 點知比我見到個紙袋，我二話不說拎起個紙袋，然後...有人想知我繼續講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13c0bbf8e97c3e93e83c7cb94d0032692007004c","tid":142434,"uid":59192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T02:50:42.000Z","msg":"哪兒來的屎...."}]}